-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#1_Brochure_la_gi\" title=\"1.\u00a0Brochure l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">1.\u00a0Brochure l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#2_Kich_thuoc_thiet_ke_Brochure_truyen_thong_la_gi\" title=\"2.\u00a0K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Brochure truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">2.\u00a0K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Brochure truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#3_Muc_dich_Loi_ich_cua_Brochure_la_gi\" title=\"3.\u00a0M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch &amp; L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a Brochure l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">3.\u00a0M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch &amp; L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a Brochure l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#Dap_ung_Dinh_huong_ban_hang\" title=\"\u0110\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \/ \u0110\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng\">\u0110\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \/ \u0110\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#Kiem_tra_Thu_hut\" title=\"Ki\u1ec3m tra \/ Thu h\u00fat\">Ki\u1ec3m tra \/ Thu h\u00fat<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#Thong_tin_truc_tiep_Su_tin_nhiem\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng tin tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \/ S\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m\">Th\u00f4ng tin tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \/ S\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#4_Cac_Loai_Gap_Cach_Su_Dung_Brochure_Khac_Nhau_la_gi\" title=\"4.\u00a0C\u00e1c Lo\u1ea1i G\u1ea5p &amp; C\u00e1ch S\u1eed D\u1ee5ng Brochure Kh\u00e1c Nhau l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">4.\u00a0C\u00e1c Lo\u1ea1i G\u1ea5p &amp; C\u00e1ch S\u1eed D\u1ee5ng Brochure Kh\u00e1c Nhau l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#Gap_mot_lan_Gap_mot_nua_hoac_Gap_hai_lan\" title=\"G\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n (G\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ho\u1eb7c G\u1ea5p hai l\u1ea7n)\">G\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n (G\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ho\u1eb7c G\u1ea5p hai l\u1ea7n)<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#Gap_ba_Gap_chu_cai\" title=\"G\u1ea5p ba (G\u1ea5p ch\u1eef c\u00e1i)\">G\u1ea5p ba (G\u1ea5p ch\u1eef c\u00e1i)<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#Gap_doi_song_song\" title=\"G\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i song song\">G\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i song song<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#Phan_tu_Gap_kieu_Phap\" title=\"Ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0 (G\u1ea5p ki\u1ec3u Ph\u00e1p)\">Ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0 (G\u1ea5p ki\u1ec3u Ph\u00e1p)<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#5_Lam_the_nao_de_phan_biet_giua_tai_lieu_quang_cao_va_to_roi_to_roi_va_to_roi\" title=\"5.\u00a0L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u1edd r\u01a1i, t\u1edd r\u01a1i v\u00e0 t\u1edd r\u01a1i\">5.\u00a0L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u1edd r\u01a1i, t\u1edd r\u01a1i v\u00e0 t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-loai-brochure-khac-nhau-la-gi.html\/#To_roi_la_gi_To_roi_so_voi_Brochure\" title=\"T\u1edd r\u01a1i l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0T\u1edd r\u01a1i so v\u1edbi Brochure\">T\u1edd r\u01a1i l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0T\u1edd r\u01a1i so v\u1edbi Brochure<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e1c phong c\u00e1ch brochure kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa brochure so v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i, t\u1edd g\u1ea5p v\u00e0 t\u1edd r\u01a1i.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15179\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15179\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15179 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.1.jpg\" alt=\"Brochure\" width=\"850\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.1.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.1-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15179\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Brochure<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Brochure_la_gi\"><\/span><span class=\"sectionnum\">1.<\/span>\u00a0Brochure l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a brochure, n\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gi\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea5p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u trang v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n ph\u00e1t cho c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i.\u00a0M\u1ed9t kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u00e0 c\u00e1c trang g\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n.<\/p>\n<p>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ban \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin.\u00a0Ch\u00fang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ho\u1eb7c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, doanh nghi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 ho\u1eb7c m\u1edbi, ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan.\u00a0T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t t\u1eadn tay, g\u1eedi qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec7n, ho\u1eb7c ph\u00e2n ph\u00e1t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15180\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15180\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15180 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.2.jpg\" alt=\"Thiet-ke-brochure\" width=\"850\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.2.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.2-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15180\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf brochure<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Kich_thuoc_thiet_ke_Brochure_truyen_thong_la_gi\"><\/span><span class=\"sectionnum\">2.<\/span>\u00a0K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Brochure truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>V\u1eady k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc brochure truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0V\u00e2ng, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n, v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1c k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1ea5p l\u00e0 8,5 \u201dx 11\u201d, 9 \u201dx 12\u201d, 8,5 \u201dx 14\u201d, 5,5 \u201dx 8,5\u201d, 11 \u201dx 17\u201d v\u00e0 11 \u201dx 25,5\u201d:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1eef: 8,5 \u201dx 11\u201d<\/strong> .\u00a0K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc letter l\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t<\/li>\n<li><strong>9 \u201dx 12\u201d<\/strong>\u00a0 Th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 v\u0103n b\u1ea3n chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n,<\/li>\n<li><strong>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p: 8,5 \u201dx 14\u201d<\/strong> . H\u00e3y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<em>k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc Legal<\/em>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00eam kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1eafng xung quanh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf tr\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i.<\/li>\n<li><strong>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc ghi nh\u1edb: 5.5 \u201dx 8.5\u201d<\/strong>\u00a0.\u00a0K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea3n ghi nh\u1edb b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a k\u00edch\u00a0<em>th\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u01b0<\/em>\u00a0.\u00a0\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t.<\/li>\n<li><strong>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc tabloid: 11 \u201dx 17\u201d<\/strong>\u00a0.\u00a0K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng n\u1ed9i dung l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c n\u1ebfp g\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u trang.<\/li>\n<li><strong>11 \u201dx 25,5\u201d<\/strong>\u00a0l\u00e0 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0Ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15181\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15181\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15181 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.3.jpg\" alt=\"Standard-brochure-size\" width=\"850\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.3.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.3-236x300.jpg 236w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.3-806x1024.jpg 806w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.3-768x976.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15181\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Standard Brochure size<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Muc_dich_Loi_ich_cua_Brochure_la_gi\"><\/span><span class=\"sectionnum\">3.<\/span>\u00a0M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch &amp; L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a Brochure l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 doanh nghi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0111ang t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a brochure l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf brochure, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch.\u00a0Vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u01b0ng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u00e0 ch\u00fang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c giao ti\u1ebfp h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh 1-1 v\u1edbi kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, ch\u00fang th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u00fai ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y \u1edf c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c l\u1ec5 t\u00e2n, kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, qu\u1ea7y h\u00e0ng ho\u1eb7c n\u01a1i kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 mang \u0111i.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dap_ung_Dinh_huong_ban_hang\"><\/span>\u0110\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \/ \u0110\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15182\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15182\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15182 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.4.jpg\" alt=\"Dinh-huong-ban-hang\" width=\"850\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.4.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.4-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.4-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15182\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khi b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ty, c\u00e1c c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p ho\u1eb7c th\u1eafc m\u1eafc c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kiem_tra_Thu_hut\"><\/span>Ki\u1ec3m tra \/ Thu h\u00fat<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u00ean c\u00e1c qu\u1ea7y b\u00e1n l\u1ebb \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u.\u00a0H\u1ecd cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ho\u1eb7c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o m\u00e0 c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng cung c\u1ea5p.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thong_tin_truc_tiep_Su_tin_nhiem\"><\/span>Th\u00f4ng tin tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \/ S\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \/ d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 m\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft b\u1ed5 sung v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c c\u00f4ng ty, t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o th\u00f4ng tin tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15183\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15183\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15183 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.5.jpg\" alt=\"Thong-ton-san-pham\" width=\"850\" height=\"585\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.5.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.5-300x206.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.5-768x529.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15183\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Cac_Loai_Gap_Cach_Su_Dung_Brochure_Khac_Nhau_la_gi\"><\/span><span class=\"sectionnum\">4.<\/span>\u00a0C\u00e1c Lo\u1ea1i G\u1ea5p &amp; C\u00e1ch S\u1eed D\u1ee5ng Brochure Kh\u00e1c Nhau l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00f3 bao nhi\u00eau ki\u1ec3u g\u1ea5p brochure?\u00a0Khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf brochure, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i brochure \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch g\u1ea5p n\u00f3.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gap_mot_lan_Gap_mot_nua_hoac_Gap_hai_lan\"><\/span>G\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n (G\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ho\u1eb7c G\u1ea5p hai l\u1ea7n)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Brochure g\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 brochure g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c g\u1ea5p r\u01b0\u1ee1i, l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i brochure \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra.\u00a0T\u00ean c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch: n\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea5y (ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, th\u01b0 ho\u1eb7c l\u00e1 c\u1ea3i) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15184\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15184\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15184 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.6.jpg\" alt=\"Gap-mot-lan\" width=\"850\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.6.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.6-247x300.jpg 247w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.6-843x1024.jpg 843w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.6-768x933.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15184\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">G\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gap_ba_Gap_chu_cai\"><\/span><span>G\u1ea5p ba (G\u1ea5p ch\u1eef c\u00e1i)<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span>Brochure g\u1ea5p ba hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 g\u1ea5p th\u01b0, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ki\u1ec3u g\u1ea5p brochure ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00f4ng ty.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15185\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15185\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15185 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.7.jpg\" alt=\"Thiet-ke-to-roi\" width=\"850\" height=\"996\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.7.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.7-256x300.jpg 256w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.7-768x900.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15185\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gap_doi_song_song\"><\/span><span>G\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i song song<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span>G\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i song song chia \u0111\u00f4i t\u1edd gi\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea5p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra hai n\u1ebfp g\u1ea5p song song \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0103n ch\u1ec9nh theo c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng.\u00a0<\/span><span>B\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh g\u1ea5p n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y chi ti\u1ebft nh\u01b0 danh s\u00e1ch s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin chung.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15186\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15186\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15186 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.8.jpg\" alt=\"G\u1ea5p-\u0111\u00f4i-song-song\" width=\"850\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.8.jpg 850w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.8-236x300.jpg 236w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.8-806x1024.jpg 806w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.8-768x976.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15186\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">G\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i song song<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Phan_tu_Gap_kieu_Phap\"><\/span><span>Ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0 (G\u1ea5p ki\u1ec3u Ph\u00e1p)<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span>The Quarter Fold, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 French Fold, mang phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o.\u00a0N\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i hai l\u1ea7n: m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n theo chi\u1ec1u d\u1ecdc, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i theo chi\u1ec1u ngang \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ed1n t\u1ea5m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Lam_the_nao_de_phan_biet_giua_tai_lieu_quang_cao_va_to_roi_to_roi_va_to_roi\"><\/span><span class=\"sectionnum\"><span>5.<\/span><\/span><span>\u00a0L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u1edd r\u01a1i, t\u1edd r\u01a1i v\u00e0 t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_roi_la_gi_To_roi_so_voi_Brochure\"><\/span><span>T\u1edd r\u01a1i l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0T\u1edd r\u01a1i so v\u1edbi Brochure<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span>T\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0T\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1edd gi\u1ea5y \u0111\u01a1n l\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 n\u1ebfp g\u1ea5p n\u00e0o, v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00f4ng tin nh\u1ecf so v\u1edbi t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.\u00a0N\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t, v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u1edd r\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in m\u1ed9t ho\u1eb7c hai m\u00e0u hai m\u1eb7t ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ee7 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef chi ph\u00ed trong ph\u1ea1m vi ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span>T\u1edd r\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in tr\u00ean kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea5y 8.5 \u2033 x 11 \u2033 ho\u1eb7c A4, ho\u1eb7c k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 g\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span>T\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn, s\u00fac t\u00edch nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecba h\u00f3a, \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m trong v\u00f2ng v\u00e0i gi\u00e2y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span>\u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf trang m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span>T\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd ng\u1eafn h\u01a1n t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, v\u00ec ch\u00fang th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n ho\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span>Ch\u00fang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, ch\u1ee9a \u00edt t\u1eeb v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span>N\u00f3i chung, t\u1edd r\u01a1i \u00edt hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n khi qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u1eb7c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0nh \u00edt th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t th\u00f4ng tin so v\u1edbi t\u1edd r\u01a1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span>C\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 h\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n, \u00e1p ph\u00edch v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng t\u01b0.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15187\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15187\" style=\"width: 850px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15187 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1.9.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1edd-r\u01a1i\" width=\"850\" height=\"566\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-con